eople:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) thus having two contr. meanings. (K.) ―         -b5-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lahu fiY Aln~aAsi $afapN", "text_ar": "لَهُ فِى النَّاسِ شَفَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He has praise,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "commendation, among the people:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lahu fiynaA $afapN HasanapN", "text_ar": "لَهُ فِينَا شَفَةٌ حَسَنَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He has a good report,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "reputation, among us."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A, K, TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_in~a $afapa Aln~aAsi Ealayoka laHasanapN", "text_ar": "اـِنَّ شَفَةَ النَّاسِ عَلَيْكَ لَحَسَنَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Verily the people's speaking of thee is good."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Lh, TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA", "text_ar": "مَا"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aHosana $afapa Aln~aAsi Ealayoka", "text_ar": "اَحْسَنَ شَفَةَ النَّاسِ عَلَيْكَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "How good is the people's speaking of thee!"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, TA.) ―         -b6-  See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$afFA", "text_ar": "شَفًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$fw", "text_ar": "شفو"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$fY", "text_ar": "شفى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "."}], "source_refs": ["K", "Msb", "T", "TA", "S", "Lth"]}, {"entry_id": "n22682", "headword_ar": "شَفَةٌ", "root": "$fw and $fY", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ", in which the deficient letter is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "w", "text_ar": "و"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K, TA,) for it has for pl